    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "The trio of aircraft pictured forms the nucleus of Delta's modern jet\nfleet. The Lockheed wide-body TriStar, powered by three Rolls-Royce\nRB211-22B Engines, features comfortable 2-by-2 seating in both First\nClass and Tourist and accommodates 250 passengers. The Wide-Ride'\nBoeing 727-232, with a seating capacity of 131 passengers, has an ultra-\nmodern sculptured interior for roomy comfort. The Douglas DC-9-32\ncarrying 90 passengers,\noperates easily and efficiently on shorter-haul\ninter-city routes served by smaller airports.\nPOSTCARD\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nDELTA IS READY WHEN YOU ARE!\n0432-01338\nPrinted in US.A\n2015,166.2522"
    ],
